map: fy_fw_pooloperation

a new generation of pool party maps, made by "EXOTIC COMMANDO"

to use it put the BSP file into: computer > (C:) drive > programfiles > steam > steamapps > "user name" > counter-strike source > Cstrike > maps

also place the sound file into: computer > (C:) drive > programfiles > steam > steamapps > "user name" > counter-strike source > Cstrike > maps > soundcache

**made for www.firewallcs.net**
